@lewismc I have created issue [1] on NumericRangeQuery. Let s address this separately. I think this PR is in good shape to be merged.
All major test cases passes without any issue. 
[1] https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GORA-555

@chanakadkb Thank you for addressing my review comments. I ll let others to have a look as well. I do have a very minor concern on test running time which is - it takes around 13 minutes to complete on my local machine. Do you think further we can improve on this? ( Reducing embedded server startup/stop etc. ) 

As per the offline chat we had, lets separately address these concerns, hadoop-commons transitive dependency issue etc. We will also probably need documentation for gora site, adding hive datastore dependencies gora-tutorial, further improve on mapping files tests, mapreduce/flink/spark workloads tests to hive datastore, test cases which currently dissabled. You can address these in separate Jira tickets. 

I think we are are good to go with the initial version hive datastore. What's your thought @lewismc ?
